\",","        description: \"Our experience as a partner in the digital transformation of companies and institutions guarantees the high efficiency of the services provided.\",","        buttonLabel: \"Transmission\")","        .orangePreview()","}"],"type":"file","highlights":[{"line":26},{"line":27},{"line":28},{"line":31},{"line":40},{"line":45},{"line":51},{"line":52},{"line":54},{"line":55},{"line":57}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-librairies":{"url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-librairies","estimatedTime":"10min","role":"project","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-onboarding-1-package-and-librairies","kind":"project","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS is exposed through an open source Swift Package hosted on GitHub, and provides several librairies for your needs."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"These librairies help to split products and make users able to select only what they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI is the only official supported framework for Apple platforms."}],"type":"topic","title":"Swift Package integration"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/Table-Of-Contents-(onboarding)/Import-of-the-Swift-Package-and-choose-its-librairies":{"url":"\/tutorials\/table-of-contents-(onboarding)\/import-of-the-swift-package-and-choose-its-librairies","role":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/Table-Of-Contents-(onboarding)\/Import-of-the-Swift-Package-and-choose-its-librairies","kind":"article","abstract":[],"type":"topic","title":"Import of the Swift Package and choose its librairies"},"tutorial-onboarding-2-2.swift":{"syntax":"swift","fileType":"swift","fileName":"InfoCard.swift","identifier":"tutorial-onboarding-2-2.swift","content":["\/\/","\/\/ Software Name: OUDS iOS","\/\/ SPDX-FileCopyrightText: Copyright (c) Orange SA",